title.narrative: Empowering New Generations to Improve Nutrition and Economic opportunities (ENGINE)

description.narrative: Empowering New Generations to Improve Nutrition and Economic opportunities (ENGINE): The overall goal of the program is to decrease maternal, neonatal and child mortality by improving the nutritional status of women and children less than 5 years through sustainable, comprehensive and coordinated evidence-based interventions.
